name: 昌多·卡努里
introduction: Chandu Kanuri is an Indian Musical Artist was born 25 May 2006 a famous Singer,Music Composer,Writer,Music Publisher,Dancer,Author,Actor,Artist,Poet And He Manages a Record Label. He Is an Hip-Hop/Rap and Pop Genre Music Maker. He is the founder of the label Chandu Kanuri Unlimited Music. He is also known for"King Of Pop". He is one of the best music composer in India. Before acting in movies, he composed some background music such as Moonu, Peaceful Rhythm and Best Of Chandu Kanuri(Original Motion Picture Soundtrack) and The Way Of Music(Original Series Soundtrack) etc. He Published Kindle Edition Books and Named, "Life Of Chandu Kanuri","Biography Of Chandu Kanuri, and So many Books. He was started his music carrier on May 2023 by releasing Tum Hi Ho(Chandu)
